I've got a few T cards available to trade.  These are generally lower grade but some are still decent looking.  I'd prefer to trade for a similar quality card that I don't have in the same set, but I collect just about everything so feel free to make an interesting offer.  You can see a list of my full collection in my signature.  Scans below, send PM with any offers.  See my C,E,D,R cards available for trade also.
